string.name: help0
string.value:
#e[To Enter the Event]#n

 If there's a notice posted in #b#ein blue#n#k saying that we're accepting participants for an event, click on #e[Paul]#n and choose #e[Yeah, let's go!]#n to enter.
 If you have already clicked on [Paul] when the event starts, then just click on [Yeah, let's go!] to enter.

 Please read the event notice before entering.
 Once the event starts, participants will be accepted as #efirst come, first serve#n until the event is full.

#eYou can't enter an event more than once within 24 hours.#n

 You won't be able to enter the event if you don't have any free slots available on your etc. inventory to receive an 'Event Trophy,' so make sure to leave a slot available.
 If you already have a #bSecret Scroll#k, please discard it before entering the event..

#r If you change channels or enter the #bCash Shop#k during the event, you'll automatically be disqualified from the event.

string.name: help0
string.value:
#e[How to Participate in this Event]#n

 There will be a notice popping up, written in #b#eBlue#n#. When that happens, click on #e[Jean]#n and click on #e[Alright, let's go.]#n to enter.
 If you have already clicked on [Jean] before the notice popped up, all you need to do is click on [Alright, let's go.] to enter.

 Please check the Event notice first before entering the event.
 Once the event notice is up, we'll be gathering up the event participants on a #eFirst-come, First-serve#n order.

 You may not participate in more than ONE event for every 24 hrs.
 You won't be able to participate in this event if you do not have the necessary free spots available for 'Participation Reward', so please make sure to leave a free etc. slot open before joining the event.
 If you possess the Scroll of Darkness, then you'll need to throw it away before participating.

#r During the event, if you happen to change the channel or use the Cash Shop while at the Event map, you won't be able to return to the event, thereby getting disqualified from the event, so please be careful on that.

string.name: help1
string.value:
#e[ Monster Attack ]#n

#e#rA BIG MONSTER ALERT!!!#k#n

 A force of evil that had been sealed up for ages have recently been let loose, and the evil monsters that have soaked up the force are planning to attack any town of their choice! This is when we all need to gather up and unite as one in defeating the monsters that may endanger the lives of mnay in the area. 
These monsters are controlled by the force of evil, and are all very powerful.

The #e#bForce of Evil#k#n that can be collected by defeating all the monsters attacking the village should be taken to the #e#bMaple Administrator#k#n.
After sealing up the monstrous force through spells, the #e#bforce of evil#k#n can then be taken to #e#bNPC The Rememberer#k#n.
Alright, now please head over to the town where the monsters have attacked, and please save the town from getting totally demolished by these evil monsters!

string.name: help0
string.value:
#e[OX Quiz]#n

Hi there, thank you for participating in our event game. Here's a little introduction about the game.

 Once you join the game, turn on the #rminimap#k by pressing #bM#k to see where the X and O are. A total of #r10 questions#k will be given, and the character that answers them all correctly wins the game.
Once the question is given, use the ladder to enter the area where the correct answer may be, be it X or O. If the character does not choose an answer or is hanging on the ladder past the time limit, the character will be eliminated. Please hold your position until [CORRECT] is off the screen before moving on. To prevent cheating of any kind, #ball types of chatting#k will be turned off during the OX quiz.

string.name: help0
string.value:
#e[Ola Ola]#n

Hi there, thank you for participating in our event game. Here's a little introduction about the game.

[Ola Ola] is a game where participants climb ladders to reach the top. Climb your way up and move to the next level by choosing the correct portal out of the numerous portals available.
The game consists of three levels, and the time limit is #b6 MINUTES#k. During [Ola Ola], you #bwon't be able to jump, teleport, haste, or boost your speed using potions or items#k.
 There are also trick portals that'll lead you to a strange place, so please be aware of those.

If you have any other question regarding this event, feel free to ask during the game.

#e[MapleStory Physical Fitness Test]#n

Hi there, thank you for participating in our event game. Here's a little introduction about the game.

[MapleStory Physical Fitness Test]is a race through an obstacle course#k much like the Forest of Patience. You can win by overcoming various obstacles and reaching the final destination within the time limit.
The game consists of #rfour levels#k, and the time limit is #b15 MINUTES#k. During the [MapleStory Physical Fitness Test], you will not be able to use #bteleport or haste#k.

If you have any other questions regarding the game, feel free to ask during the game.

string.name: help0
string.value:
#e[Snowball]#n

Hi there, thank you for participating in our event game. Here's a little introduction about the game.

[Snowball]consists of two teams, Maple Team and Story Team, and the two teams duke it out to see #bwhich team rolled the snowball further and bigger in a limited time#k. If the game cannot be decided within the time period, then the team that rolled the snowball further wins.
To roll up the snow, attack it by pressing "C". 
#bAll long-range attacks and skill-based attack will not work here; only the close-range attacks will#k.
If a character touches the snowball, he/she'll be sent back to the starting point. Attack the snowman in front of the starting point to prevent the opposing team from rolling the snow forward. This is where a well-planned strategy works, as the team will decide whether to attack the snowball or the snowman.

If you have any other questions regarding the game, feel free to ask during the game.

string.name: help0
string.value:
#e[MapleStory Minigame Challenge]#n

Hi there, thank you for participating in our event game. Here's a little introduction about the game.

[MapleStory Minigame Challenge] is a tournament that determines the best of minigames.
 Up to 32 users can participate in this, and it will go on a head-to-head format, all the way until 1 final winner remains.

#kThe matchup will be randomly selected in a round of 32, and the game will move on to round of sweet 16, great 8, the final 4, then the finals.
#b If there aren't enough users around, or if a user leaves the tournament in the middle of the game, the opponent will be awarded with the win and will move on.
#r Also, if there happens to be a tie, then both players will be eliminated from the tournament.

#kAfter each game, there will be a quick resting period before a new game begins, so all players that have ended the game early should wait for a few minutes.

#b After the finals is over, the 1st and 2nd place will be sent to the podium where the winners will be awarded with a reward.#kAfter the finals is over, the portals on the podium and at the very bottom of the map will be open for your exit, and #rall users will be kicked out of the map after 5 minutes. The players that receive the rewards should do so within the 5 minute period.

#k[MapleStory Minigame Challenge] is there for all players to compete, fair and square.
#bAll users are advised to participate in this game with fair play in mind.

#k All skills will be blocked during this tournament.

For other questions, feel free to ask during the game.

string.name: help0
string.value:
#e[Coconut Harvest]#n

 Hello. Welcome to #r[Coconut Harvest]#k.
 Here are the instructions. In [Coconut Harvest], there are two teams. One is #bMaple Team#k and the other is #bStory Team#k. The team that collects more #rCoconuts#k in #r5 minutes#k wins the game. If the game ends in a #b[draw]#k, then #r2 minutes of extra time#k will be given. If the game ends in a draw after 2 minutes of extra time, the game will just end as a draw. In this case, nobody gets the prize.
#r You will not be able to use long-range attacks or skills.#k If you don't have a close-range weapon, please purchase one from the NPC in the event map. 
There are many #btraps & obstacles#k all over the map. You will get #rdamaged#k if you are hit by coconuts or obstacles, so please use potions and keep an eye on your HP. If you run out of HP, you are going to be left out of the game.

 During the game, players will be affected with the same amount of damage from obstacles regardless of the character's level, weapon, and upgrade. 

 Some coconuts never fall and some just break. Only the coconuts that fall down will count. 
 There are also hidden portals on the wreath shell, so please use them wisely.

string.name: help0
string.value:
#e[G Coconut Season]#n

 Hello Maplers. Thank you for joining us in the event #r[G Coconet Season]#k.
 Please allow us to briefly explain to you about the event.

 Event [G Coconet Season] will divide users in to #bMapleTeam#kand #bStoryTeam#k and #rTeam who earns more coconuts wins#k. Time limit for the game will be #r3 minutes#k. If the result is draw in the first game, extra 1 minute will be added. Game will automatically end draw if there is another draw. 
#r Long range and skill attacks are not available and only the normal attacks will be possible.#k If you do not have normal attack weapons, please purchase the weapons from the NPC in the event map.

 There are #bobstacles and traps#k in the map. If you are hit by Jr. Neki, you will be #rdamaged#k so beware of that and use the potions properly. If died, you will be disqualified for the event game.

 Skill will not be used in the event maps and regarless of the level, weapon and option, #bsame attack level will be applied.#b

 The point will be given to the #bteam who hits coconut the last before it is dropped.#k There are coconuts which will not drop no matter how many time you hit and some of them will burst when hitting since it is too ripe. Only ones that drop will be counted for points.
 There are hidden portals turban shells, make sure you take advantage of that.
